abstract: The advocacy group Guns Down America graded 15 banks based on their support for the gun industry. Most received dismal appraisals.

abstract: Madden, who has four Olympic medals, and her horse Breitling LS won the World Cup show jumping finals last year. They are back again.
snippet: Madden, who has four Olympic medals, and her horse Breitling LS won the World Cup show jumping finals last year. They are back again.
lead_paragraph: With riders galloping their horses toward obstacles the size of S.U.V.s and then suddenly turning, show jumping is a sport of timing and finesse, but it’s not for the faint of heart.
